gomodel:SYNGO_2629  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099033 replaced by GO:0098944" , "Rationale: Figure 3: \"Subcellular distribution of ABHD17\"\nFig.3D: \"ABHD17 proteins show a very similar distribution pattern to TfR, which was colocalized with ABHD17 on the recycling endosomes (Fig. 3B,D) and is recycled between the cytoplasm and plasma membrane in the dendritic spine (Kennedy et al., 2010).\". Experimental description: \"Differential subcellular distribution of FLAG-tagged ABHD proteins and Lypla2. Note that some populations of ABHD17A localized at the postsynaptic membranes labeled by pan-Shank antibody (red) in 14 DIV rat hippocampal neurons.\"\n\n- \"The cDNAs of rat ...ABHD17A (NM_001006983), ... ABHD17B (NM_146096), ABHD17C (NM_133722), ...\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
